Legcy STRAIGHT

The legacy-STRAIGHT is a collection of speech analysis, modification and resynthesis tools. 

Release note
This is a copy of the latest version which was distributed by the first author (Hideki Kawahara) to academic communities. The version is named STRAIGHTV40_007. The last update was July 17, 2016. The legacy-STRAIGHT has also been licensed by Kansai TLO for commercial use. The all licensees agreed to make the legacy-STRAIGHT open to public after July 15, 2018. 

Acknowledgement
The legacy-STRAIGHT was supported by many coauthors, contributors and funding agencies. 

Hideki Kawahara,
July 16, 2018
